
---

### **.gitignore**

```gitignore
# --------------------
# Compiled Object Files
# --------------------
*.o
*.obj

# --------------------
# Executables
# --------------------
*.exe
*.out
*.app
*.bin

# --------------------
# Build Directories
# --------------------
/build/
/Debug/
/Release/

# --------------------
# IDE / Editor Specific
# --------------------
.vscode/
.idea/
*.suo
*.user
*.vcxproj*
*.ncb
*.sdf

# --------------------
# OS Specific
# --------------------
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# --------------------
# Temporary Files
# --------------------
*~
*.swp
*.tmp
